    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 2,
