      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> and <strong>peanut butter</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>fish sauce</strong>,<strong> lime leaves</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>– this is your<strong> peanut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1624630541309-x200.jpg",
